activity.rule_One: 1、Each users can submit a maximum of 5 names, including Chinese names and English names. Repeated submissions are not allowed. activity.rule_Two: 2、If the name suggestion is finally adopted, a mysterious gift will be provided by the project party.
activity.rule_Three: 3、Once the solicitation is adopted, the relevant copyrights, usage rights, publishing rights, etc. shall be owned by TELTLK.
